Rating: 4
I have made this three times for different people in the last week - so easy and yummy! I add another 1/2 c of beans, add a small can of diced green chilis to the bean/corn/onion mix, and reduce each kind of cheese by about 1/4 c - I like the ratios better this way. Also, instead of oil I use cooking spray on the top tortillas and sprinkle the cayenne on top. Will definitely make this again and again, great for lunch, a light dinner, or as appetizers.

