Rating: 4
4 forks with the following changes: add 1 tsp. each of cumin & chili powder and 1/2 tsp. salt. Brush top with oil, 1/8 tsp. cayenne and juice from one lemon to kick it up. Then bake for 5 min more in a 400 oven. It's so easy & soooooo good!

